{"tid":156980,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"突發!!李斯特城獲下季出戰歐聯資格","createTime":"2017-03-15T06:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T09:07:02.000Z","uid":34993,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03d391f893e3e8af641d9c9ac4e4d8f89bd72392","tid":156980,"uid":34993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T06:52:23.000Z","msg":"為獎勵李斯特城首次出戰歐聯即成功晉級十六強，英超賽會決定將來季其中一個歐聯資格破例送予李斯特城，以作表揚。有人歡喜有人愁，英超賽會亦宣佈落實《出戰歐聯球隊品質監控條例》，於本賽季歐聯分組賽出局的熱刺已被永久禁止參與歐聯賽事。<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n拿斯利：對十六強出局並不陌生<br />\n阿仙奴獲永久十六強參賽權　唯不設晉級資格"},{"pid":"7adfe68002699c36c77e2f8202845786f34a1f4c","tid":156980,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T06:53:43.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"70a635a0aec15160dd54f07884f26e6b37b55b6e","tid":156980,"uid":2676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T06:54:06.000Z","msg":"拿斯利：對十六強出局並不陌生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fafc3102658a2785203091be725c961e6600a0dd","tid":156980,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T06:54:39.000Z","msg":"報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d862fdc48a54ea3057138d9508262c479b09540","tid":156980,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T06:55:01.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc86bfcabbb771f9f22b9106463ea0ebde7a9e8","tid":156980,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T06:55:45.000Z","msg":"熱刺第一次打歐聯都八強喎"},{"pid":"964eba80af7a4cf7fca4a02dbf4456217bbd8633","tid":156980,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T06:57:09.000Z","msg":"李城可能今年奪冠，下年有得踢呢"},{"pid":"c86b5434c7c